README for wine 20050524


REQUIREMENTS


PRE-INSTALL


POST-INSTALL

1. Run the 'wine.inst' script to install the configuration files.
   (or run 'wineprefixcreate' and simply copy the configuration 
   file from /usr/share/wine/configs/config)

2. Edit ~/.wine/config to customize mount locations under wine.


PRECAUTION

It is recommmended that you clean out your wine-config directory 
after each new release, as old registry data can cause problems.
